VIEW: Historical command (not implemented)

The original game's website help index listed a "view" topic.
Recovered player notes and archives do not document a distinct
server-side view command separate from look, examine, eq, or score.

Use these instead:
  look / examine   inspect a room or object
  eq               see worn and wielded gear
  score            character sheet
  picture show     see a player's ASCII portrait

No view command is implemented in this recreation.

SEE ALSO: look, examine, eq, score, picture
